03:40.409 --> 03:48.620
We the members of Reformation Baptist Church hereby affirm this covenant with one another by God's grace for our good and for God's glory.

03:48.660 --> 03:53.106
Having been brought as we believe by the spirit of God and divine grace,

03:53.474 --> 04:01.403
to repent and believe in the Lord Jesus Christ as the Lord savior and supreme treasure of our lives.

04:02.384 --> 04:23.186
And upon the profession of our faith, having been baptized in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, we do in the presence of God in this assembly, solemnly and joyfully covenant with one another as one body in Christ to glorify God by worshiping together and making disciples.

04:23.650 --> 04:32.220
God has covenanted within the Godhead Father, Son, and Holy Spirit to save a people for Himself for His own glory.

04:32.680 --> 04:34.583
